fields.Title: SEAFORT ORB / quiet on the island
fields.Placement: island, two meters right of pine tree in sector 1

fields.Title: Shivers: "Of great importance to the few who..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Of great importance to the few who attend.

fields.Title: You: "To the east..."
fields.Dialogue Text: To the east...

fields.Title: Cuno: ""What?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "What?"

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "On the islet? There is almost no wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: On the islet? There is almost no wind, just snow quietly falling on the reeds. Bulrushes swaying on the waterline, long dried leaves chafing against each other.

fields.Title: You: "Ahead..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Ahead...

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "Air flows out of a pillbox window...."
fields.Dialogue Text: Air flows out of a pillbox window. There is very little there. The air cossets flowers on a meadow? Absolute silence. Reeds motionless. Bulrushes motionless.

fields.Title: You: ""Have you noticed how quiet it is?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Have you noticed how quiet it is?"

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "On the islet? There is almost no wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: On the islet? There is almost no wind under the rain quietly falling on the reeds. Bulrushes swaying on the waterline, long dried leaves chafing against each other. The soft raindrops...

fields.Title: Shivers: "The great ghost of the air is holdi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The great ghost of the air is holding its breath.

fields.Title: You: "Below the silence?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Below the silence?

fields.Title: You: ""It... hurts a bit. Maybe the banda..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It... hurts a bit. Maybe the bandage is off?"

fields.Title: Conceptualization: "Like a silent orchestra tuning -- a..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Like a silent orchestra tuning -- at the beginning of some major work.

fields.Title: You: ""It's really fucking silent on this..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's really fucking silent on this island."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It can happen -- is that why we're..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It can happen -- is that why we're stopping?"

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Momentarily the sounds are swept aw..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Momentarily the sounds are swept away. Pain shoots up your right foot and into your groin...

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "On the islet? There is almost no wi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: On the islet? There is almost no wind, just the light movement of air through the reeds. Bulrushes swaying on the waterline, long dried leaves chafing against each other.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""It is -- is that why we're stoppin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It is -- is that why we're stopping?"

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "The far away roar of the city, dist..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The far away roar of the city, distant like today's dream. Before it, the sound of sand. The low tide filtered through its grains... a bird tending to its feathers.

fields.Title: You: "Beyond that... further north..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Beyond that... further north...

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "This is where a lesser man would st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is where a lesser man would stop to think about the pain shooting up his right leg and into his groin -- not you, you're concentrated on how...

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "A drop of rain falls on a black log..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A drop of rain falls on a black log. Of an extinguished camp-fire.

fields.Title: Cuno: "He squints at you. "Is that why we'..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He squints at you. "Is that why we're stopping? So you can *bitch about the bandage*?"

fields.Title: You: ""No, I was listening to something.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I was listening to something."

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "The dry grass crackles under your f..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The dry grass crackles under your feet as you stop. Far away birds' wings touch the still surface of the sea...

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "This is where a lesser man would st..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is where a lesser man would stop to think about the pain shooting up his right leg and into his groin -- not you, you're concentrated on how...

fields.Title: You: ""It's pretty silent on this island.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's pretty silent on this island."

fields.Title: You: "[Stop listening.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Stop listening.]

fields.Title: You: "Underneath the flutter..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Underneath the flutter...

fields.Title: You: "To the west..."
fields.Dialogue Text: To the west...

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "A jitter. A sound impatient to happ..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A jitter. A sound impatient to happen, but not yet in this world.

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "A silent hiss, sea air moving throu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A silent hiss, sea air moving through the needles of a pine tree.

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "Raindrops fall on water, strangely..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Raindrops fall on water, strangely quiet, forming circles in the distance...

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "Snow falls on the water, melting aw..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Snow falls on the water, melting away without even a whisper.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""Yes?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yes?"

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "The flock of quail departs; now mor..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The flock of quail departs; now more than a hundred metres away... a hundred and two... a hundred and five...

fields.Title: Logic: "No, it's just your imagination. You..."
fields.Dialogue Text: No, it's just your imagination. You can't hear such things.

fields.Title: You: ""It's really fucking silent on this..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's really fucking silent on this island."

fields.Title: You: ""Mhm. Wait. I have to listen to one..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mhm. Wait. I have to listen to one more thing."

fields.Title: You: ""It's pretty silent on this island.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "It's pretty silent on this island."

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Yeah. Spooky-ass island. That's ho..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Yeah. Spooky-ass island. That's how it is on spooky-ass islands. Silent and shit."

fields.Title: Cuno: "The kid shrugs. He sniffs, audibly..."
fields.Dialogue Text: The kid shrugs. He sniffs, audibly -- then, silence.

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "You hear some kind of limb fidget,..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You hear some kind of limb fidget, producing an imperceptible tick...

fields.Title: Inland Empire: "We are way out now... Way out in th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: We are way out now... Way out in the West.

fields.Title: You: ""Sorry. Let's move." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry. Let's move." [Leave.]

fields.Dialogue Text: "It... hurts a bit. Maybe the bandage is off?"

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "A flake of snow falls on an extingu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A flake of snow falls on an extinguished camp-fire. Hiss...

fields.Title: You: ""Mhm. Wait. I have to listen to one..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Mhm. Wait. I have to listen to one more thing."

fields.Title: Pain Threshold: "Momentarily the sounds are swept aw..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Momentarily the sounds are swept away. Pain shoots up your right foot and into your groin...

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "Col Do Ma Ma Daqua."
fields.Dialogue Text: Col Do Ma Ma Daqua.

fields.Title: Cuno: ""Fuckin' spooky, yeah. Is what it i..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Fuckin' spooky, yeah. Is what it is."

fields.Title: Perception (Hearing): "A low hum. The air slowly moves thr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: A low hum. The air slowly moves through a concrete box -- through its ancient slits and cracks. Resonating. Hollow. A big building.

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: "The lieutenant nods, in silence."
fields.Dialogue Text: The lieutenant nods, in silence.

fields.Title: You: ""Cuno...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Cuno..."

fields.Title: You: ""Have you noticed how quiet it is?""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Have you noticed how quiet it is?"

fields.Title: You: ""Sorry. Let's move." [Leave.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: "Sorry. Let's move." [Leave.]

fields.Title: You: "[Open your eyes, stop listening.]"
fields.Dialogue Text: [Open your eyes, stop listening.]

fields.Title: You: ""No, I was listening to something.""
fields.Dialogue Text: "No, I was listening to something."

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I have -- is that why we're stoppi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I have -- is that why we're stopping?"

fields.Title: Cuno: "He shrugs. "Spooky-ass island. That..."
fields.Dialogue Text: He shrugs. "Spooky-ass island. That's how it is on spooky-ass islands. Silent and shit."

fields.Dialogue Text: What is that flutter?
